## 4.5 Strategic Planner

### 4.5.1 Purpose

Generate and maintain the 1-10 year strategic plan using genetic algorithms, constrained by capacity envelopes from the tactical model.

### 4.5.2 Implementation

```typescript
interface StrategicPlannerConfig {
  horizonYears: number;          // 10
  granularity: 'MONTHLY' | 'QUARTERLY';
  populationSize: number;        // 100
  generations: number;           // 500
  mutationRate: number;          // 0.1
  eliteCount: number;            // 10
}

interface StrategicAllocation {
  trainId: string;
  pmTypeId: string;
  targetQuarter: string;  // e.g., '2028-Q2'
  estimatedHours: number;
  estimatedCost: number;
